    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I have written an article about <a href=\"http://ssw.jku.at/dcevm/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">DCEVM</a>: <a href=\"https://mufumbo.wordpress.com/2012/02/02/spring-mvc-velocity-dcevm/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Spring-mvc + Velocity + DCEVM</a> </p>\n\n<p>I think it's worth it, since my environment is running without any problems. </p>\n"
