      "body" : "I would never suggest otherwise. In fact - the only reason I bring this up is because there is no &quot;individual&quot; license anymore. I was able to get my company to pay for my work license. I then also paid for a personal license, for my personal use, for over 3 years. But when the price when north of $260 a year, that became impractical. This is the best solution for me (and others), but I would have also kept paying for it if the price was reasonable."
